        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The magic in your blood is unpredictable. When you make your daily preparations, roll [[/r 1d12]] twice and consult the following list:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Acid Arrow];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Blur];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Laughing Fit];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Humanoid Form];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Illusory Object];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Mirror Image];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Resist Energy];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.See the Unseen];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shatter];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Noise Blast];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Gecko Grip];</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Telekinetic Maneuver].</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You can cast each of those two spells once during the following day (or one spell twice if you rolled doubles) as 2nd-rank divine innate spells.</p>"
